Spencer and Lauren flew out to Morocco last week and stayed at the boot camp’s luxury five-star villa just outside Marrakech.

Every morning they were woken at 6am and had an hour of exercise before breakfast. At 8.30am they would have an hour and a half of cardio training – boxing or spinning, followed by a snack at 10am, then circuit training at 10.30am until 12.

Lunch would be an hour and then they would have long hikes, followed by team games and then yoga and stretching exercise. The evening meal would follow at 7.30pm.

